headline: Why IAC (IAC) Stock Is Trading Lower Today
summary: Shares of digital media conglomerate IAC (NASDAQGS:IAC) fell 3.1% in the afternoon session after Oppenheimer downgraded the company's stock to 'Perform' from 'Outperform,' citing concerns about its valuation.
